      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's kinda hard to talk really. it feels tight in my chest too. i have some Zyrtec here, how much should i take to make the wheezing stop quickly? i don't really want to go to a doctor if i can help it, i just wanna feel better so i can finish my homework.",
